title: Six Star Pro Nutrition Casein Protein Powder, 100% Pure Casein, Triple Chocolate, 2.0 Pounds
description: Six Star Pro Nutrition Casein Protein delivers 40 grams of premium protein, including slow-digesting casein protein powder, which helps feed your muscles with a continued flow of amino acids (the building blocks of muscle). 100% of the casein protein component in Six Star Pro Nutrition Casein Protein is high-quality casein protein, which is a slow-release form of protein and is rich in amino acids. This makes it perfect to take between meals and before bed. How to Make the Perfect Casein Protein Shake Tip - Try blending with ice, your favorite fruit, juice, peanut butter, or anything else you enjoy for a delicious smoothie. Directions - Take 1 to 2 scoops (1 to 2 servings) two times daily. Take 1 serving preferably before bed. Mix each scoop with 10 to 12 oz. of skim milk or water to taste
